%% Diagram: Resource Hints Timing
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Browser
    participant N as Network
    participant V8 as JS engine
    Note over B,V8: preload (high prio, fetch only)
    B->>N: GET chunk.js
    N-->>B: bytes
    Note over B: HTTP cache, not parsed
    B->>V8: parse + compile on first import
    Note over B,V8: modulepreload (high prio, fetch + parse)
    B->>N: GET module.js
    N-->>B: bytes
    B->>V8: parse, compile, store in module map
    Note over B: import resolves instantly
    Note over B,V8: prefetch (idle prio, fetch only)
    B-->>N: GET next-route.js
    N-->>B: bytes during idle
    Note over B: warm cache for next nav
